This is useful because retrieval practice strengthens memory.

4
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:12,000
Moving on, spaced repetition schedules review before forgetting is complete.

5
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:15,000
To summarize, combine recall questions with spaced review sessions.
